## Prohibited Actions
- Storing user data on the server
- Exposing user information to the host
- Implementing analytics or tracking
- Using third-party services that collect user data

## Required Patterns
- Client-side storage for all user progress (localStorage/IndexedDB)
- If sync is needed: client-side encryption with user-controlled keys

